Little Neck Parkway, west side, near 74th Avenue, showing the Henry Cox (Cocks) house of 1873-1891. In 1891 the farm contained 104 acres and stretched north from Motor Parkway from where views 2 and 3 were taken.

View 1: Eugene L. Armbruster Collection 1922

Views 2, 3: P.L. Sperr
March 1, 1927
